{"commentv2": 1, "number": 8, "id": 1666507, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Valko", "body": "This, ladies and gentlemen, is the greatest dwarf who ever lived.\r\n\r\nHe is Muradin, and compared to him you are but lowly peasants. You know why there will never be a \"Sargaeras\" expansion? BECAUSE MURADIN ALREADY KILLED HIM. WITH HIS BEARD.\r\n\r\nHe was hit in the head by a MAGICAL shard of ice shot at him by a MAGICAL sword that just so happens to DEVOUR SOULS, and just got up and walked it off. After surviving this even like a badass, he walked out into the snow and SINGLE HANDEDLY KILLED A GIGANTIC, FANGED, ICE-WORM OF DEATH.\r\n\r\nHe, folks, is the sheer awesome incarnate. None may match the almighty power of Muradin! DWARVES 4 LIFE.", "date": "2012-05-13T14:31:13-05:00", "rating": 29, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Does Legion count as a 'Sargaeras' expansion?", "creationdate": "2016-08-24T07:57:47-05:00", "id": 962880, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1666507, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Artora", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Present the reforged frostmourne to him in IronForge and see what he says.", "creationdate": "2016-12-17T17:33:06-06:00", "id": 1017163, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1666507, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "akunderdog", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "And i'm gonna go ahead and shoot him with pellet gun", "creationdate": "2017-12-29T11:02:28-06:00", "id": 1091616, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1666507, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "2000polas", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true,