{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 2541507, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "RokudoRinne", "body": "If you approach Muradin with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=128292/blades-of-the-fallen-prince]Blades of the Fallen Prince[/url], you will trigger an interesting conversation.\n\n\"[i]What is this blasphemy, <player>? How dare you reforge that cursed blade, the very sword that damned Lordaeron and its prince? I warned Arthas not to touch Frostmourne, and now I'm warning you: cast those things into the sea before they damn us all.[/i]\"", "date": "2017-12-20T04:50:00-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2017-12-20T04:52:58-06:00", 3, "RokudoRinne"]}
