{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2127092, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "goaskmalice", "body": "This is one of several NPCs that can randomly spawn in your garrison each day. They will appear in the entryway of your level 3 town hall. Some of the NPCs will offer quests while others will be traders. Everyone on your realm will have the same trader if they get the trader, but whether you get the trader or a questgiver will be up for individuals is random each day. \n\n[i][b]You can use a questgiver or trader at someone else's garrison.[/b][/i] Have them invite you into a group, and then right-click your own portrait and select \"view leader's garrison\". This will take you to their garrison and you can use whatever NPC they have there. \u2605\n\nOccasionally [npc=91016] will appear in your menagerie and offer the bonus pet battle daily, [quest=38299]. There are several different versions of her, so please see [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=91014/erris-the-collector#comments:id=2122420]this comment[/url] for more info on her and her pet teams.\n\nTraders will offer a daily quest to exchange 50 of a prof mat (ore, leather, fur, etc) for 25x [item=120945]. After that, you can buy primals from them using the mats (5xmats for 1xprimal spirit), as well as some recipes for that profession. Quests you pick up will be turned into [npc=81492], so you do not need to return to someone else's garrison to turn them in if you didn't pick up the quest in your own garrison.\n\n[hr]\n[b]\u2605 \u2605 \u2605 [u]Questgivers[/u] \u2605 \u2605 \u2605[/b]\n[hr]\n[b] [npc=89763] is a questgiver offering the following quests:[/b]\n\u2605 [u]Weekly Raid Quests[/u]\n[ul][li][quest=37762][/li]\n[li][quest=37763][/li]\n[li][quest=37764][/li]\n[li][quest=37765][/li]\n[li][quest=37766][/li]\n[li][quest=37767][/li]\n[li][quest=37758][/li][/ul]\n\u2605 [u]Daily Dungeon Quests[/u]\n[ul][li][quest=37789][/li]\n[li][quest=37790][/li]\n[li][quest=37791][/li]\n[li][quest=37792][/li]\n[li][quest=37793][/li]\n[li][quest=37794][/li]\n[li][quest=37795][/li]\n[li][quest=37796][/li][/ul]\n\n [b] [npc=89793] is a questgiver offering the following quests:[/b]\n[ul][li][quest=37848][/li]\n[li][quest=37973][/li]\n[li][quest=37881][/li]\n[li][quest=37914][/li]\n[li][quest=37788][/li]\n[li][quest=37941][/li][/ul]\nCompletion of these quests leads to the awarding of the achievement [icon name=faction_horde][/icon] [achievement=9836] /  [icon name=faction_alliance][/icon] [achievement=9825] and the follower [follower=465].\n\n[hr]\n[b]\u2605 \u2605 \u2605 [u]Traders:[/u] \u2605 \u2605 \u2605[/b]\n[hr]\n\u2605 [b]Tailoring[/b]: Fur Trader [icon name=faction_alliance][/icon] [npc=91025]  /  [icon name=faction_horde][/icon] [npc=91034]\n[ul][li]Offers [quest=38293] for 25 [item=120945].[/li]\n[li]Sells\n1x [item=120945] for 5x [item=111557]\n[item=122549] for 60x [item=111557]\n[item=122716] for 60x [item=111557][/li][/ul]\n\u2605 [b]Leatherworking[/b]: Leather Trader [icon name=faction_alliance][/icon] [npc=91024] / [icon name=faction_horde][/icon] [npc=91033]\n[ul][li]Offers  [quest=38287] for 25 [item=120945].[/li]\n[li]Sells\n1x [item=120945] for 5x [item=110609]\n[item=122547] for 60x [item=110609]\n[item=122715] for 60x [item=110609][/li][/ul]\n\u2605 [b]Blacksmithing/Jewelcrafting/Engineering[/b]: Ore Trader  [icon name=faction_alliance][/icon] [npc=90894] or [icon name=faction_horde][/icon] [npc=91030]\n[ul][li]Offers [quest=38243] for 25 [item=120945].[/li]\n[li]Sells:\n1x [item=120945] for 5x [item=109119]\n[item=122546] for 60x [item=109118]\n[item=122550] for 60x [item=109118]\n[item=122551] for 60x [item=109118]\n[item=122712] for 60x [item=109118]\n[item=122552] for 60x [item=109119]\n[item=122554] for 60x [item=109119]\n[item=122705] for 60x [item=109119]\n[item=122714] for 60x [item=109119][/li][/ul]\n\u2605 [b]Alchemy/Inscription[/b]: Herb Trader  [icon name=faction_alliance][/icon] [npc=91404] or [icon name=faction_horde][/icon] [npc=91031]\n[ul][li]Offers [quest=38296] for 25 [item=120945].[/li]\n[li]Sells:\n1x [item=120945] for 5x [item=109129]\n[item=122710] for 60 [item=109127]\n[item=122600] for 10 [item=122600]\n[item=122599] for 10 [item=122600]\n[item=122605] for 10 [item=122600]\n[item=122553] for 20 [item=114931]\n[item=122548] for 20 [item=114931]\n[item=122713] for 20 [item=114931][/li][/ul]\n\u2605 [b]Enchanting[/b]: Dust Trader [icon name=faction_alliance][/icon] [npc=91020] or  [icon name=faction_horde][/icon] [npc=91029]\n[ul][li]Offers [quest=38290][/li]\n[li]Sells:\n1x [item=120945] for 5x [item=109693]\n[item=122711] for 5x [item=111245]\n[/li][/ul]\n\nI think I've finally collected all of the information on this, but I will update this comment if I discover anything new. You may also be interested in checking out the wonderful guide to 6.1 garrison visitors [url=http://www.wowhead.com/guides/professions/wod/professions-in-patch-6-1#daily-garrison-visitors]here[/url].", "date": "2015-03-02T12:14:55-06:00", "rating": 23, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just Brackenspore. Always Brackenspore. Brackenspore is love, Brackenspore is life.", "creationdate": "2015-04-15T18:29:03-05:00", "id": 863223, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2127092, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Tribunal", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2015-03-14T09:59:45-05:00", 2, "goaskmalice"]}
