{"commentv2": 1, "number": 11, "id": 1009640, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "258919", "body": "After completing [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=13417]The Brothers Bronzebeard[/url] in the Storm Peaks, Yorg Stormheart is revealed by Brann to be Muradin Bronzebeard. Shortly after regaining his memory of his true identity, Muradin is met by his other brother, King Magni Bronzebeard, who travelled to Northrend to find Muradin.\r\n\r\nAfter their brief reunion, Brann leaves to continue his research into the titan's secrets, Magni returns to his people in Ironforge. Muradin believes it to be his fault that Arthas became the Lich King, because he did not stop it. Therefore, Muradin sets off towards Icecrown to set things right. In Icecrown Citadel, he helps in the attack on Arthas' most powerful troops, eventually helping to slay the Lich King, fulfilling his vow.", "date": "2010-03-31T20:57:54-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
